            <div class="archive__item-excerpt">
              <p>TermIt runs on Institute of Planning and Development of Prague (IPR) since 2021. TermIt was originally created in the project OPPPR and IPR tested its usability â€“ to describe Metropolitan plan and help to relate it to the legislation. Nowadays, TermIt serves for systemization of terminology in other projects, e.g. Uniform Interchangeable Format of the Digital Technical Map (JVF DTM) and Building Intelligence Model (BIM).</p>

            </div>
          

          
            <p><a href="https://termit.fel.cvut.cz/ipr/#/public" class="btn ">See TermIt on IPR</a></p>
          
